[h2][b]Changelog[/b][/h2]

[h2][9.00.08] - 2026-04-19[/h2]
[list]
[*] [b]Added[/b]
[list]
[*] Workforce resource consumption: food, medicine, and other wares consumed only by workforce now appear in the Resources group.
[*] Empire balance: an optional [i]All stations:[/i] sub-row shows empire-wide production and consumption for each Product and Intermediate ware with a coloured surplus/deficit balance. Available in single-station view only.
[/list]
[*] [b]Improved[/b]
[list]
[*] Data cache throttle: expensive C API calls are reused for [b]dataRefreshInterval[/b] UI ticks before recomputing. Configurable in the Extensions options menu (default 3, range 1-10).
[/list]
[/list]
